properties.text:
Reach the top to [color=#ff5555]DEFEAT[/color] the dragon!

How to play:

- [color=#00aaff]\[Arrows][/color]: move, jump and climb ladders
- [color=#00aaff]\[Space][/color]: throw water to extinguish fire entities
- [color=#00aaff]\[Space][/color] next to a stalactite: refill your bucket

Press [color=#00aaff]\[Space][/color] to start...
